items.title: Code Switching Muslim w/ Arun Rath
items.content:encoded: Wow, what an incredible month - we are super excited to have been invited to the All Things Considered Weekend Edition with Arun Rath. We had a great conversation which you can listen to at the audio below and be sure to read the article too (excerpt below!).
items.content:encodedSnippet:
Wow, what an incredible month - we are super excited to have been invited 
to the All Things Considered Weekend Edition with Arun Rath. We had a great
